&lt;h1 id="google-should-pull-an-android-on-facebook"&gt;Google should pull an Android on Facebook&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jul 7 2011&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Android&amp;rsquo;s best weapon against iOS is that it&amp;rsquo;s a much more open platform. iOS&amp;rsquo; elegant user experience comes at a cost – developers have to suffer through approval delays, rejections, private APIs, rules against advertising, and shutdowns. Android, on the other hand is open to carriers, users, and developers.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>谷歌应该对 Facebook 采取 Android 策略</title><link>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/zh/google-should-pull-an-android-on-facebook.zh/</link><pubDate>Thu, 07 Jul 2011 04:23:18 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://linguista.cn/person/naval/zh/google-should-pull-an-android-on-facebook.zh/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/person/naval/orig/google-should-pull-an-android-on-facebook/"&gt;原文(English)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
